description: This big bold truck is supplying Nashville with some nourishing noshes that satisfies foodies and health nuts alike. Behind the wheel of Healthy Grub, you’ll find Johnna & Chris, a super cool couple with a mutual entrepreneurial spirit, a shared passion for their community, as well as a love for cooking up tasty food that’s actually great for you.Their menu changes week by week but with a selection of Flatbread Pizza, Organic Salads, Wraps, and more, there’s always something real yummy to eat. You're also sure to find that their fresh fruity smoothies make for quite the perfect fuel to get you through your day. So believe all the hubbub and come out to Healthy Grub for food that your body will thank you for.
name: Healthy Grub
